<th align="left">Function</th>
<th align="left">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><em>L3/4 Translation Function</em></td>
<td align="left">Translates up to and including the IP and transport layer (e.g., UDP, TCP) protocol headers, while leaving all higher layer protocol headers and payloads untouched.</td>
</tr>
